<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8380595>
    dc:description "Figs 6-22. Stenogephyra gen. n. 6-21. S. torrida sp. n. 6. 7. Male head in frontal view. B. Male antenna. 9. Female antenna. 1O-1B. Male terminaha. 10. Male genitalia in lateral view. 11. Epandrium and cerci in dorsal view. 12. Epandrium, cerci and ventral epandrial sclerite in ventral view. 13. Gonocoxites with gonostyli in ventral view. 14. Left gonocoxite with ~onostylus and aedeagal complex in dorsal view. 15. Right gonocoxite with gonostylus in mterior view. 16. Aedeagus in lateral view. 17. Sternite B. lB. Tergite B. 19-21. Female terminalia. 19. Sternite B. 20. Subgenital plate and vaginal apodeme. 21. Tergite B, tergite 10 and cerci in dorsal view. 22. S. minuta sp. n., male antenna. Scale: 1 mm for 6 and 7,0,5 mm for the rest." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8380595/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

